      "section_title": "CONCLUSION",
      "unit_id": null,
      "text": "DRAK2 is a serine\u2013threonine kinase implicated in the regulation of apoptosis and is negatively regulated by COX-2 in vitro and in vivo, suggesting a novel mechanism for the effect of COX-2 on cancer cell survival."
